            "container_id": "cntr_69d593622e3c8190aafa136cf9fd0a2f0c217d605e8fe333",
            "code": "import numpy as np\nfrom scipy.optimize import fsolve\n\n# Define the equation\ndef equation(x):\n    return np.sin(x) + x**2 - 42\n\n# Let's estimate a range where x^2 = 42, so x ~ ±sqrt(42)\nx_guess_pos = np.sqrt(42)   # positive root near 6.48\nx_guess_neg = -np.sqrt(42)  # negative root near -6.48\n\n# Use fsolve to find the roots\nroot_pos = fsolve(equation, x_guess_pos)[0]\nroot_neg = fsolve(equation, x_guess_neg)[0]\n\nroot_pos, root_neg",
